graph LR
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller<br/>kubeflow/notebook-controller]

    %% External Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.22.0+]
    NotebookController -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.17.0]
    NotebookController -->|metrics| PrometheusClient[Prometheus client_golang v1.18.0]
    NotebookController -->|service mesh<br/>optional| Istio[Istio v1alpha3 API]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|shared utilities| KubeflowCommon[kubeflow/common<br/>Go module]
    NotebookController -->|configuration| ConfigMapConfig[ConfigMap: config<br/>USE_ISTIO, ISTIO_GATEWAY, ADD_FSGROUP]
    NotebookController -->|configuration| ConfigMapCuller[ConfigMap: notebook-controller-culler-config<br/>ENABLE_CULLING, CULL_IDLE_TIME]
    NotebookController -->|routing<br/>when USE_ISTIO=true| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway<br/>kubeflow/kubeflow-gateway]

    %% Generated Resources
    NotebookController -->|creates| StatefulSet[StatefulSet<br/>Notebook Pod]
    NotebookController -->|creates| Service[Service<br/>ClusterIP]
    NotebookController -->|creates<br/>when USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualService[VirtualService<br/>Istio routing]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| NotebookController
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|notebook creation| NotebookController
    ServiceMesh[Service Mesh] -.->|mTLS enforcement| NotebookController

    %% External Services
    NotebookController -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    NotebookController -->|metrics export| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
    NotebookController -->|activity checks| NotebookPods[Notebook Pods<br/>8888/TCP HTTP]

    %% CRDs
    NotebookController -->|watches/manages| NotebookCRD[Notebook CRD<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]

